10
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:31,320
And don't worry, this is definitely not an
idea torn from the pages

11
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:35,710
of some Philip K. Dick dystopian sci-fi story.

12
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:36,589
To understand it,

13
00:00:36,589 --> 00:00:37,920
let's take a look at a movie based on

14
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:40,309
