murder of Sarah Marks.”

17
00:00:47,510 --> 00:00:49,469
In the movie Minority Report,

18
00:00:49,469 --> 00:00:52,249
crime is stopped before it happens,

19
00:00:52,249 --> 00:00:57,559
because it's predicted by three "precogs."

20
00:00:57,559 --> 00:00:59,519
