32
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,800
Seriously, they are planning to create precrime,
though.

33
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:24,020
China is already a surveillance state.

34
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:28,260
The Communist Party monitors every aspect
of every citizen's life.

35
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:32,340
Here's China Uncensored Precrime expert Harold
Finch on how it works.

36
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:36,580
“The government gave itself the power to
read every email,

37
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:37,930
listen to every cell phone,

38
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:42,560
