it all,

39
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,070
something that could pick the terrorists out

40
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:46,700
of the general population before they could
act.”

41
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:48,590
Oh wait, sorry,

42
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:51,470
that's from the fictional TV drama Person
