64
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:52,069
and figure out how to use it to prevent crime.

65
00:02:52,069 --> 00:02:54,200
So can they?

66
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:58,139
Well, that's where the China Electronics Technology
comes in.

67
00:02:58,139 --> 00:03:01,579
They're one of China's largest state-owned
defense contractors.

68
00:03:01,579 --> 00:03:04,319
They've been given the job to, as Bloomberg
puts it,

69
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:06,849
“Develop software to collate data on jobs,

70
00:03:06,849 --> 00:03:08,840
hobbies, consumption habits, and other

71
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,230
behavior of ordinary citizens to predict

72
00:03:11,230 --> 00:03:13,219
terrorist acts before they occur.”

73
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,980
Is this even possible?

74
00:03:15,989 --> 00:03:19,389
Well, a recent research paper by mathematicians
at

75
00:03:19,389 --> 00:03:23,099
University College London suggests that with
enough data,

76
00:03:23,099 --> 00:03:26,029
patterns of behavior emerge that you can use

77
00:03:26,029 --> 00:03:29,239
to predict certain terrorist acts.

78
00:03:29,239 --> 00:03:32,760
So anyone who engages in suspicious or dangerous
behavior,

79
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:37,049
such as using a VPN to jump the Great Firewall
of China,

80
00:03:37,049 --> 00:03:39,980
and look up information on known terrorist
ringleader

81
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:41,489
the Dalai Lama,

82
00:03:41,489 --> 00:03:45,090
might find themselves "invited to tea" with
authorities.

83
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:46,959
Did I mention is this is for fighting terrorism,

84
00:03:46,959 --> 00:03:49,950
and absolutely not for clamping down on dissent?

85
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:52,730
The government would definitely not use it
to, say,

86
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:55,499
predict anti-government protests,

87
00:03:55,499 --> 00:03:58,010
and send in the police before they begin.

88
00:03:58,010 --> 00:04:00,540
Because China's constitution guarantees freedom
of

89
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:03,430
speech, and the press, and assembly.

90
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:07,939
Now a lot about this precrime program remains
unknown to the outside world,

91
00:04:07,939 --> 00:04:09,359
and to the Chinese people—

92
00:04:09,359 --> 00:04:11,760
including when it will be put in effect.

93
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:15,239
And while other countries are trying to create
similar programs,

94
00:04:15,239 --> 00:04:18,009
China's program is likely to be more successful.

95
00:04:18,009 --> 00:04:21,139
According to their definition of success,
at least.

96
00:04:21,139 --> 00:04:24,050
That's because the Party doesn't have to worry
about pesky things like

97
00:04:24,050 --> 00:04:26,680
